data.description: ASSUMABLE VA LOAN!  This beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom house is the perfect place for families of any size to call home. With a large family room downstairs and a spacious game room upstairs, everyone can have their own space to enjoy. You'll enjoy maximum privacy with the primary bedroom located downstairs, while the remaining bedrooms are upstairs. The primary closet features a full closet organizer.  The kitchen is every chef's dream, complete with a microwave, stovetop, oven, dishwasher, and granite counters to make meal preparation a breeze. You can entertain guests or relax in the sun in the large backyard. Plus, just minutes away from Fischer Park, you'll have endless opportunities to enjoy the great outdoors. This home is conveniently located near New Braunfels shopping and entertainment, as well as major highways for easy access to all your favorite destinations. With no HOA, you can truly make this house your own. Schedule your visit today and make your dream home a reality!
